## Phase 2: Backend — Service Layer & API Integration

---

### 2.1 Services

#### [NEW] `AiPredictionService.php`
**Path**: `app/Services/AiPredictionService.php`

Core service that:
1. Calls the 3 HF Space APIs (`/predict` endpoints)
2. Handles SSE response parsing (same pattern as existing `ChatbotService`)
3. Maps API responses to DB models
4. Saves predictions + history
5. Triggers notifications on high-risk results
6. Implements retry/timeout logic for sleeping HF Spaces

Key methods:
- `predictGDM(User $user, array $inputOverrides = []): GestationalDiabetesPrediction`
- `predictPreeclampsia(User $user, array $inputOverrides = []): PreeclampsiaPrediction`
- `predictPretermBirth(User $user, array $inputOverrides = []): PretermBirthPrediction`
- `getHistory(User $user, ?string $diseaseType = null): Collection`

#### [NEW] `PatientDataCollectorService.php`
**Path**: `app/Services/PatientDataCollectorService.php`

Auto-populates prediction input fields from existing patient data:

| Target Field | Source |
|---|---|
| [age](file:///d:/Final_Project_Implementation/Final_Project_Front_And_Back/Back-end/app/Models/User.php#66-71) | `UserProfile.date_of_birth` → calculated age |
| `height_cm` | `UserProfile.height` |
| `weight_kg` | `UserProfile.weight` (or latest `WeightEntry`) |
| `bmi` | `UserProfile.calculateBMI()` |
| `blood_pressure` | `UserProfile.blood_pressure_systolic/diastolic` |
| `no_of_pregnancy` | `User.pregnancies()->count()` |
| `family_history` | `UserProfile.medical_history` JSON parsing |
| `pcos` | `UserProfile.chronic_diseases` array search |
| `previous_gdm` | Check [gestationalDiabetesPredictions](file:///d:/Final_Project_Implementation/Final_Project_Front_And_Back/Back-end/app/Models/User.php#151-155) history |
| `gestational_diabetes` | Check active pregnancy GDM prediction results |
| `pregnancy_week` | `Pregnancy.current_week` from active pregnancy |

Key methods:
- `collectForGDM(User $user): array` — returns pre-filled form data
- `collectForPreeclampsia(User $user): array`
- `collectForPretermBirth(User $user): array`

---

### 2.2 Controllers

#### [NEW] `AiPredictionController.php` (Patient)
**Path**: `app/Http/Controllers/Api/Patient/AiPredictionController.php`

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `hub()` | `GET /patient/ai-center` | Hub data: model info + latest results summary |
| `getPreFillData()` | `GET /patient/ai-center/{model}/prefill` | Auto-filled form data from profile/trackers |
| `predictGDM()` | `POST /patient/ai-center/gdm/predict` | Run GDM prediction |
| `predictPreeclampsia()` | `POST /patient/ai-center/preeclampsia/predict` | Run PE prediction |
| `predictPretermBirth()` | `POST /patient/ai-center/preterm/predict` | Run PTB prediction |
| `getHistory()` | `GET /patient/ai-center/history` | All predictions timeline |
| `getPredictionDetail()` | `GET /patient/ai-center/predictions/{id}` | Single prediction detail |

#### [NEW] `DoctorAiPredictionController.php` (Doctor)
**Path**: `app/Http/Controllers/Api/Doctor/DoctorAiPredictionController.php`

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `patientPredictions()` | `GET /doctor/patients/{id}/ai-predictions` | View all AI predictions for a patient |
| `addComment()` | `POST /doctor/ai-predictions/{id}/comment` | Doctor comment on prediction |
| `predictionStats()` | `GET /doctor/ai-center/stats` | Summary stats across doctor's patients |

#### [NEW] `AdminAiAnalyticsController.php` (Admin)
**Path**: `app/Http/Controllers/Api/Admin/AdminAiAnalyticsController.php`

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `dashboard()` | `GET /admin/ai-center/analytics` | Overall AI usage stats |
| `modelStats()` | `GET /admin/ai-center/models/{model}/stats` | Per-model breakdown |
| `riskDistribution()` | `GET /admin/ai-center/risk-distribution` | Risk level charts data |

