### 2.4 Routes

#### [MODIFY] [patient.php](file:///d:/Final_Project_Implementation/Final_Project_Front_And_Back/Back-end/routes/patient.php)
Add AI Center route group:
```php
Route::prefix('ai-center')->controller(AiPredictionController::class)->group(function () {
    Route::get('/', 'hub');
    Route::get('/{model}/prefill', 'getPreFillData');
    Route::post('/gdm/predict', 'predictGDM');
    Route::post('/preeclampsia/predict', 'predictPreeclampsia');
    Route::post('/preterm/predict', 'predictPretermBirth');
    Route::get('/history', 'getHistory');
    Route::get('/predictions/{id}', 'getPredictionDetail');
});
```

#### [MODIFY] [doctor.php](file:///d:/Final_Project_Implementation/Final_Project_Front_And_Back/Back-end/routes/doctor.php)
```php
Route::prefix('ai-center')->controller(DoctorAiPredictionController::class)->group(function () {
    Route::get('/stats', 'predictionStats');
    Route::get('/patients/{id}/predictions', 'patientPredictions');
    Route::post('/predictions/{id}/comment', 'addComment');
});
```

#### [MODIFY] [admin.php](file:///d:/Final_Project_Implementation/Final_Project_Front_And_Back/Back-end/routes/admin.php)
```php
Route::prefix('ai-center')->controller(AdminAiAnalyticsController::class)->group(function () {
    Route::get('/analytics', 'dashboard');
    Route::get('/models/{model}/stats', 'modelStats');
    Route::get('/risk-distribution', 'riskDistribution');
});
```

